<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="min-h-dvh text-green-700">
  <main class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-6xl flex-col gap-10 px-4 py-8 sm:px-6 lg:px-10 lg:py-14">
    <section class="text-center">
      <p class="mb-4 inline-flex rounded-full border border-green-200 bg-white px-4 py-1 text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-gray-500">Chat de ajuda</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tight sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-green-700">Chat Taiksu</h1>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-sm text-gray-500 sm:text-lg">Plataforma de atendimento em tempo real para suporte ao cliente com mensagens, midia e metricas.</p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row">
        <a href="/auth/login" class="rounded-xl bg-green-400 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-green-500">Entrar com SSO</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-green-100 bg-white p-5">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-green-700">Tempo real</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">Mensagens instantaneas via SSE com atualizacao continua.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-green-100 bg-white p-5">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-green-700">Dashboard</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">Metricas para acompanhar uso, salas e mensagens.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-green-100 bg-white p-5">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-green-700">Midia</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">Envio de audio, video, imagens e documentos no chat.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-green-100 bg-white p-5">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-green-700">Status de digitacao</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">Sinaliza quando alguem esta digitando em tempo real.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-green-100 bg-white p-5">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-green-700">Leitura</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">Confirmacao de leitura para melhorar o fluxo de suporte.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-green-100 bg-white p-5">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-green-700">Widget</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500">Integracao com sites e apps via widget JavaScript.</p>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
